sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Admin or Guard
    participant UI as JavaFX Event Request Screen
    participant API as Spring Boot EventRequestController
    participant Service as EventRequestService
    participant DAO as EventRequestDAO / EventRequestDeviceDAO
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Audit as AuditLogDAO

    User->>UI: Enter event header and device line items
    UI->>API: POST /event-requests
    API->>Service: create event request
    Service->>Service: validate document type, dates, line items
    Service->>DAO: save request and line items
    DAO->>DB: INSERT event_requests; INSERT event_request_devices
    Service->>Audit: fn_write_audit_log EVENT_REQUEST_CREATED
    API-->>UI: Event request saved

    User->>UI: Verify event device line item
    UI->>API: PUT /event-requests/{id}
    API->>Service: update verification/status
    Service->>DAO: update event_request_devices or event_requests
    DAO->>DB: UPDATE event_request_devices / event_requests
    API-->>UI: Updated request state
